{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-js","path":"/operators/continuous-deployment/docs/inclusions_explained.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1f76275a-92b7-597a-8908-5924cb773569","html":"<h1 id=\"inclusions-explained\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inclusions-explained\" aria-label=\"inclusions explained permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Inclusions explained</h1>\n<p>It is likely that your team does not have <code class=\"language-text\">get</code> access to all namespace scoped resources.\nThis can be an issue when deploying apps to a namespace in a cluster, because ArgoCD will\nattempt to discover all namespace scoped resourced and be denied. To avoid this, we limit\nArgoCD to discover the resources that are available to project admins, these should be added\nunder the <code class=\"language-text\">resource.inclusions</code> ArgoCD configurations in <code class=\"language-text\">manifests/overlays/&lt;target_env&gt;/configs/argo_cm/resource.inclusions</code>.</p>\n<p>If your application contains resources that a project <code class=\"language-text\">admin</code> does not have permissions\nto list/edit then you can request that a cluster admin deploy aggregated roles to add\nsuch permissions. See here for an <a href=\"https://github.com/argoproj/argo-events/blob/master/manifests/cluster-install/rbac/argo-events-aggregate-to-admin.yaml\">example</a>.</p>\n<p>Once having done so, you can make a PR with these resources added onto the <code class=\"language-text\">resource.inclusions</code>\nlist.</p>\n<h2 id=\"resources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#resources\" aria-label=\"resources permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Resources</h2>\n<p>Read more about exclusion/inclusions <a href=\"https://argoproj.github.io/argo-cd/operator-manual/declarative-setup/#resource-exclusioninclusion\">here</a>.</p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/continuous-deployment/blob/master/docs/inclusions_explained.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"1f76275a-92b7-597a-8908-5924cb773569"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","3000541721"]}